name: BetaBlockersGDMTForHypertension
title: Beta blockers GDMT for Hypertension
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Beta blockers listed as guideline-rected medication therapy (GDMT) in the 2017 ACC AHA Hypertension guideline.),(Data Element Scope: INTENTIONALLY LEFT BLANK),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNorm codes (RxCUIs) corresponding to the drugs listed in Figure 5 of the guideline: carvedilol, metoprolol tartrate, metoprolol succinate, nadolol, bisoprolol, propranolol, and timolol),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
